Here can be found all the generic objects which are used by the skills
bin dir. E.g. the cleric' tree spell object. Etc.



/obj/skills/classes
These are class specific items that are used by the classes. E.g. the 
paladin's war horse, and the paladin 'class' auto_load object.

/obj/skills/affils
Here can be found the auto_load objects for each affiliation. It is 
important that all affiliation objects go in here as to the generic
calls made back to them by the system.
